OL,5, Hundreds of Amazon workers in Coventry 
OL,6, have begun a three-day strike in a     
OL,7, dispute over pay.                      
OL,9,FThe GMB union said 600 members walked  
OL,10,Fout at 06:30 BST and will not return   
OL,11,Funtil Tuesday, with further action due 
OL,12,Fto take place from 21 to 23 April.     
OL,14,FMembers are calling for a pay rise from
OL,15,F#10.50 to #15 an hour, although the    
OL,16,Funion is not recognised by the US firm.
OL,18,FAmazon had previously said that minimum
OL,19,Fpay had recently risen by 10% and by   
OL,20,Fmore than 37% since 2018.              
